title: Obama promises to help Texas with flooding - CNN Video
text: Running updates: Storms slam Houston, kill 22 in Texas, Oklahoma, Mexico By Eliott C. McLaughlin, CNN Texas and Oklahoma are praying for a respite following four days of epic rainfall that has killed nine people. Another 13 people died in Ciudad Acuña, Mexico, when a ferocious tornado ripped through the border town of 180,000. More from US
